CONTEXT arithmetic
CONSTANTS
    add, sub, mul, divv, modd, expp, neg, cardc, minc, maxc
AXIOMS
    @axm1 add = 2 + 3
    @axm2 sub = 7 − 2
    @axm3 mul = 2 ∗ 4
    @axm4 divv = 9 ÷ 2
    @axm5 modd = 9 mod 2
    @axm6 expp = 2 ^ 3
    @axm7 neg = −5
    @axm8 cardc = card({1, 2, 3})
    @axm9 minc = min({1, 2, 3})
    @axm10 maxc = max({1, 2, 3})
END
